Class JIJConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.reexon.reexon.lib.eclipse.JIJConstants

  • final class JIJConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants used in the Jar-in-Jar loader. Some of these are duplicated in JIJConstants in the source for the Runnable Jar File Export Wizard: org.eclipse.jdt.internal.ui.jarpackagerfat.
